in 1845, pp. 189 and 193, that for Virgil to grant ecclesiastical authority is totally foreign to \softline
anything we have read in this poem.  In an entirely similar mode, Singleton (}{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 Journey to Beatrice}{\plain \fs24 \f1  \softline
[Cambridge: Harvard University Press, 1967 (1958)]), pp. 64-69, cites (not Ponta or Scartazzini \softline
